channel.title: Domains
channel.description:
Well heres the story, I just cashed out $25 from moola. Anyway I want to buy a couple domain names. The network solutions $40 is a bunch of bullshit and I know you can get .com for like $6 at some sites...
Where do you buy your domains/wheres cheapest?
NO HOSTING!!!
Also, I am kinda worried about private domain records so I dont get freaks at my house but can you just put fake info in the signup?
